ng-lasting, fade-resistant and crafted to give your wall a clean, premium look with zero effort.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis poster blends perfectly into bedroom, living room, gaming setup or workspace décor. Easy to frame, perfect for collage walls, and ideal for anyone who loves aesthetic room vibes, minimal design and high-quality prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA great pick for personal use or gifting — made to match your vibe and elevate your space.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394462253352,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394462286120,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394462318888,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/GhostCallOfDutyGameSet3PieceSet_2.webp?v=1764072413"},{"product_id":"the-upside-down-awakens-stranger-things-01-3-piece-set","title":"The Upside Down Awakens | Stranger Things #01 | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"1027\"\u003eStep into the dark world of the Upside Down with this electrifying \u003cstrong data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"744\"\u003eStranger Things concept poster\u003c\/strong\u003e, featuring powerful fantasy-style artwork inspired by the show’s iconic Season 4 villain — \u003cstrong data-start=\"836\" data-end=\"845\"\u003eVecna\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003cbr data-start=\"846\" data-end=\"849\"\u003eSurrounded by glowing red lightning and floating D20 dice, the poster fuses the essence of \u003cstrong data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"962\"\u003eDungeons \u0026amp; Dragons\u003c\/strong\u003e with the sinister atmosphere of Hawkins’ most terrifying threat.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1029\" data-end=\"1367\"\u003eAt the forefront stands a heroic party — an archer, a warrior, a bard, and a fire-wielding mage — symbolizing the fearless energy of the show’s beloved characters as they face off against supernatural evil.\u003cbr data-start=\"1235\" data-end=\"1238\"\u003eThe intense red palette, dynamic poses, and cinematic lighting make this piece a perfect centerpiece for any Stranger Things fan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1369\" data-end=\"1491\"\u003eIdeal for bedrooms, gaming rooms, studios, and collectors, this poster turns your space into a gateway to the Upside Down.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394461925672,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394461958440,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394461991208,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/W_0d4843cc-f724-4617-a668-e4d6dfeefe7c.webp?v=1764594072"},{"product_id":"jinx-enemy-arcane-3-piece-set","title":"Jinx Enemy | Arcane | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"481\" data-end=\"813\"\u003eBring the chaos, attitude, and raw energy of \u003cstrong data-start=\"526\" data-end=\"534\"\u003eJinx\u003c\/strong\u003e into your space with this striking \u003cem data-start=\"570\" data-end=\"587\"\u003eArcane-inspired\u003c\/em\u003e “ENEMY” poster. Designed with a bold neon-red palette, grunge textures, and an atmospheric moonlit backdrop, this artwork captures Jinx’s rebellious spirit and her iconic duality — the hero they loved, the enemy they created.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"815\" data-end=\"1154\"\u003eJinx sits front and center on her throne-like structure, staring down with a mix of defiance and vulnerability, perfectly matching the tone of the hit Arcane soundtrack \u003cem data-start=\"984\" data-end=\"994\"\u003e“Enemy.”\u003c\/em\u003e The massive ENEMY typography behind her adds weight and intensity, while the glitched lyrics on the corner tie the entire visual together with emotional depth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1156\" data-end=\"1365\"\u003ePrinted in razor-sharp quality with vivid colors, this poster is the perfect addition to bedrooms, gaming rooms, studios, or any setup that celebrates Arcane, League of Legends, or high-stylized character art.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394461761832,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394461794600,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394461827368,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/Wall-splitw.webp?v=1764937106"},{"product_id":"arcane-jinx-graffiti-split-3-piece-set","title":"Arcane Jinx | Graffiti Split | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"537\" data-end=\"857\"\u003eBring pure chaotic energy to your room with this explosive \u003cstrong data-start=\"596\" data-end=\"645\"\u003eArcane Jinx graffiti-style split panel poster\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003cbr data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"649\"\u003eFeaturing Jinx in full punk-rock mode with her iconic long braids, neon cyan–purple highlights, and a weaponized guitar, this artwork captures her wild, unpredictable spirit straight from the streets of Zaun.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"859\" data-end=\"1181\"\u003eThe bold graffiti tags, distressed textures, and high-contrast color palette make the piece feel raw, rebellious, and alive — exactly how Jinx would leave her mark. The 3-piece split design adds a dramatic, modern display effect perfect for gaming setups, bedrooms, studios, and collectors who want powerful visual impact.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1183\" data-end=\"1363\"\u003ePrinted in high-resolution on premium fade-resistant material, this poster set is a must-have for lovers of \u003cstrong data-start=\"1291\" data-end=\"1301\"\u003eArcane\u003c\/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong data-start=\"1303\" data-end=\"1324\"\u003eLeague of Legends\u003c\/strong\u003e, punk aesthetics, and edgy wall decor.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394461270312,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394461303080,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394461335848,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/ArcaneJinxGraffitiSplit3PieceSet_3.webp?v=1765027426"},{"product_id":"king-steve-harrington-stranger-things-01-3-piece-set","title":"King Steve Harrington | Stranger Things #00 | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"241\" data-end=\"575\"\u003eCelebrate the unbeatable charm and fearless attitude of \u003cstrong data-start=\"297\" data-end=\"311\"\u003eKing Steve\u003c\/strong\u003e with this stunning, high-detail concept poster inspired by his iconic heroic moments.\u003cbr data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"400\"\u003eThis artwork captures Steve in full battle-ready mode leather jacket, nail-studded bat, and that signature confident stare that made him a fan-favorite protector of Hawkins.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"803\"\u003eSet against a dramatic red-and-blue Upside Down–inspired background, the poster blends \u003cstrong data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"688\"\u003egraphic-novel energy\u003c\/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"712\"\u003ecinematic lighting\u003c\/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong data-start=\"718\" data-end=\"737\"\u003ebold typography\u003c\/strong\u003e to create a powerful statement piece for any Stranger Things fan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"805\" data-end=\"1024\"\u003eEvery detail, from the stylized shadows to the glowing red atmosphere, reflects the intensity of the world Steve fights to protect reminding everyone why he is more than just “\u003cstrong\u003eKing Steve\u003c\/strong\u003e”… he is the heart of the team.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-end=\"1491\" data-start=\"1369\"\u003eIdeal for bedrooms, gaming rooms, studios, and collectors, this poster turns your space into a gateway to the Upside Down.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394460254504,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394460287272,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394460320040,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/stevew1.jpg?v=1766055004"},{"product_id":"the-ghost-samurai-3-piece-set","title":"THE GHOST | Samurai | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"479\" data-end=\"800\"\u003eBring a bold, cinematic \u003cstrong data-start=\"503\" data-end=\"533\"\u003eJapanese samurai aesthetic\u003c\/strong\u003e to your setup with this \u003cstrong data-start=\"558\" data-end=\"594\"\u003eTHE GHOST 3-Panel Split Wall Set\u003c\/strong\u003e. Featuring a lone warrior in a stormy, fog-filled landscape with striking red calligraphy, this artwork gives your wall a clean \u003cstrong data-start=\"723\" data-end=\"745\"\u003eminimal + powerful\u003c\/strong\u003e vibe that looks insane above a desk or gaming station.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"802\" data-end=\"1008\"\u003eThe split layout creates a premium “gallery wall” feel with dramatic negative space and a strong center focus—perfect for \u003cstrong data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"1007\"\u003egaming rooms, bedrooms, studios, offices, and anime\/Japan-inspired decor lovers\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1010\" data-end=\"1033\"\u003eWhat you’ll receive\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul data-start=\"1034\" data-end=\"1176\"\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1034\" data-end=\"1071\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1036\" data-end=\"1071\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1036\" data-end=\"1071\"\u003e1 Set = 3 Panels (split design)\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1072\" data-end=\"1134\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1074\" data-end=\"1134\"\u003eHigh-detail print with sharp contrast + minimalist ink style\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1135\" data-end=\"1176\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1137\" data-end=\"1176\"\u003eIdeal for wide walls above a desk\/setup\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1178\" data-end=\"1215\"\u003eSize options (final trimmed size)\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1216\" data-end=\"1363\"\u003eWe print on full sheets with white borders, then \u003cstrong data-start=\"1265\" data-end=\"1282\"\u003emanually trim\u003c\/strong\u003e for a clean finish—so the sizes below are the \u003cstrong data-start=\"1329\" data-end=\"1362\"\u003efinal set size after trimming\u003c\/strong\u003e:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul data-start=\"1364\" data-end=\"1483\"\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1364\" data-end=\"1402\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1366\" data-end=\"1402\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1366\" data-end=\"1383\"\u003eA4 Sheet Set:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cstrong data-start=\"1384\" data-end=\"1402\"\u003e24.5 × 11.5 in\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1441\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1405\" data-end=\"1441\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1405\" data-end=\"1422\"\u003eA3 Sheet Set:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cstrong data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1441\"\u003e34.5 × 16.5 in\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1442\" data-end=\"1483\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1444\" data-end=\"1483\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1444\" data-end=\"1464\"\u003e13×19 Sheet Set:\u00